5000|$|The Special Operations & Research Division (SORD) {{is located}} in Las Vegas, NV. SORD conducts basic and applied {{research}} in atmospheric dispersion, particle re-suspension, particle deposition, {{and the effects of}} airborne particles on <b>atmospheric</b> <b>opacity.</b> The Division supports issues of mutual interest to NOAA and the Department of Energy that relate to the Nevada Test Site, its atmospheric environment, and its emergency preparedness and emergency response activities.|$|E
